About the Author

Brief summary:

This website was created by Six of Crows superfan, Jiana Malaya J. Mateo, or Aya Mateo for short. She loved the book series so much she wanted to create a way to acces good fanart for this specific fandom only, and be able to do it quickly. This is what inpspired this website.
